999
00:47:02,320 --> 00:47:04,840
 neće blagosloviti lažnu jakost,

1000
00:47:04,840 --> 00:47:06,880
 neće blagosloviti tvoj posao

1001
00:47:06,880 --> 00:47:08,000
 ako postaje maska,

1002
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:10,820
 neće blagosloviti tvoj hod

1003
