1005
00:47:13,220 --> 00:47:14,280
 ako je to maska.

1006
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,460
 Neće to blagosloviti.

1007
00:47:15,460 --> 00:47:16,200
 Neće Bog sve.

1008
00:47:16,200 --> 00:47:16,920
