1010
00:47:18,480 --> 00:47:19,540
 mi krenemo nešto raditi,

1011
00:47:19,540 --> 00:47:20,380
 smo uopće pitali

1012
00:47:20,380 --> 00:47:21,320
 da li to treba ići,

1013
00:47:21,320 --> 00:47:23,340
 da li mi bježimo od nečeg drugog

1014
00:47:23,340 --> 00:47:24,640
 jer bježimo od svoje slabosti

1015
00:47:24,640 --> 00:47:26,020
 i onda Bog neka blagoslovi,

1016
00:47:26,020 --> 00:47:27,240
 idemo i tako propada

1017
00:47:27,240 --> 00:47:28,520
 Božje pomazanje

1018
00:47:28,520 --> 00:47:29,520
 i rasipamo milost.

1019
00:47:29,520 --> 00:47:30,560
 Dakle,

1020
00:47:30,560 --> 00:47:32,700
 Bog neće blagosloviti

1021
00:47:32,700 --> 00:47:33,480
 našu masku.

1022
00:47:33,480 --> 00:47:35,940
 Bog ti ne može

1023
00:47:35,940 --> 00:47:37,560
 povjeriti blagoslove

1024
00:47:37,560 --> 00:47:39,380
 ako si ti u bjegu od sebe.

1025
00:47:39,380 --> 00:47:41,200
 Rasipaš blagoslov.

1026
00:47:41,200 --> 00:47:44,820
 I sve se to događa

1027
00:47:44,820 --> 00:47:45,700
 u jednom mjestu

1028
00:47:45,700 --> 00:47:47,980
 koje se zove Penuel.

1029
00:47:47,980 --> 00:47:50,500
 Ovo mjestu Jakov nadijene

1030
00:47:50,500 --> 00:47:51,320
