1031
00:47:51,320 --> 00:47:52,840
 jer reče

1032
00:47:52,840 --> 00:47:54,220
 vidje Boga lice mu lice

1033
00:47:54,220 --> 00:47:55,360
 i na životu ostadog

1034
00:47:55,360 --> 00:47:56,460
 sunce nad njim

1035
00:47:56,460 --> 00:47:57,620
 bilo ogranulo

1036
00:47:57,620 --> 00:47:58,940
 kad je prošao Penuel.

1037
00:47:58,940 --> 00:48:00,320
 Sunce ogranulo

1038
00:48:00,320 --> 00:48:01,640
 kad je prošao Penuel.

1039
00:48:01,640 --> 00:48:03,360
 Hramo je zbog kuka.

1040
00:48:03,360 --> 00:48:05,080
 Hramo je

1041
00:48:05,080 --> 00:48:06,180
 do kraja svog života.

1042
00:48:06,180 --> 00:48:08,500
 Zato izrelci

1043
00:48:08,500 --> 00:48:09,460
