1049
00:48:14,360 --> 00:48:15,340
 bio iščašen

1050
00:48:15,340 --> 00:48:16,240
 u kukovnoj tetivu.

1051
00:48:16,240 --> 00:48:17,660
 Ovo nije etnološki podatak

1052
00:48:17,660 --> 00:48:18,740
