1053
00:48:18,740 --> 00:48:20,640
 gastronomska informacija

1054
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,340
 nego ima teološko značenje

1055
00:48:22,340 --> 00:48:23,180
 u Svetom pismu.

1056
00:48:23,180 --> 00:48:24,680
 Penuel znači

1057
00:48:24,680 --> 00:48:25,360
 Božje lice

1058
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:26,000
 a Božje lice

1059
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:26,740
 u Starom zavitu

1060
00:48:26,740 --> 00:48:28,220
