1061
00:48:28,220 --> 00:48:29,380
 I kaže

1062
00:48:29,380 --> 00:48:30,720
 kad je prošao Penuel

1063
00:48:30,720 --> 00:48:32,840
 kad je Jakov svladan

1064
00:48:32,840 --> 00:48:33,620
 kad je došao

1065
00:48:33,620 --> 00:48:34,720
 u svoju autentičnost

1066
00:48:34,720 --> 00:48:35,640
 kad je došao

1067
00:48:35,640 --> 00:48:36,280
 u svoju istinu

1068
00:48:36,280 --> 00:48:37,000
 u svoju slabost

1069
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:38,120
 kad je prihvatio sebe

1070
00:48:38,120 --> 00:48:39,640
 kad ga je Bog nadvlado

1071
00:48:39,640 --> 00:48:40,220
 i kad imao

1072
00:48:40,220 --> 00:48:42,700
