 onda je prošlo sunce.

1077
00:48:48,740 --> 00:48:49,840
 došlo je

1078
00:48:49,840 --> 00:48:50,660
 novi dan

1079
00:48:50,660 --> 00:48:51,600
 nova zora

1080
00:48:51,600 --> 00:48:53,120
 novo razdoblje života.

1081
00:48:53,120 --> 00:48:55,280
 Mi imamo neka

1082
00:48:55,280 --> 00:48:56,640
 tako krive pojmanja

1083
00:48:56,640 --> 00:48:57,560
 o duhovnosti

1084
00:48:57,560 --> 00:49:00,000
 sunce neće ograniti

1085
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:02,840
 sunce će ogranuti

1086
00:49:02,840 --> 00:49:03,820
 kad meni sve krene

1087
00:49:03,820 --> 00:49:06,680
 kad se sve vrati na staru

1088
00:49:06,680 --> 00:49:07,960
 sve što mi sad ne ide

1089
00:49:07,960 --> 00:49:09,680
 sve će se to

1090
00:49:09,680 --> 00:49:10,360
 odjednom nestati

1091
00:49:10,360 --> 00:49:13,580
 i onda će sunce ogranuti

1092
00:49:13,580 --> 00:49:15,860
 neće tako sunce ogranuti

1093
00:49:15,860 --> 00:49:16,960
 u našem životu

1094
00:49:16,960 --> 00:49:18,580
 jer Jakov je

1095
00:49:18,580 --> 00:49:20,520
 nastavio šepati

1096
00:49:20,520 --> 00:49:21,560
 ako ste gledali

1097
00:49:21,560 --> 00:49:22,100
 Chosen

1098
00:49:22,100 --> 00:49:24,340
 znate onu famoznu scenu

1099
00:49:24,340 --> 00:49:25,640
 kada gospodin

1100
00:49:25,640 --> 00:49:26,960
 govori s Jakovom

1101
00:49:26,960 --> 00:49:28,320
 to je razlog

1102
00:49:28,320 --> 00:49:29,180
 zašto on šepa

1103
00:49:29,180 --> 00:49:30,940
 i zašto ga gospodine

1104
00:49:30,940 --> 00:49:31,500
 oslobađa

1105
00:49:31,500 --> 00:49:32,440
 toga i ne ozdravlja

1106
00:49:32,440 --> 00:49:33,460
 kaže zašto je

1107
00:49:33,460 --> 00:49:34,680
 veće svjedočanstvo

1108
00:49:34,680 --> 00:49:36,540
 da vide tvoju slabost

1109
00:49:36,540 --> 00:49:38,140
 i ljubav

1110
00:49:38,140 --> 00:49:40,180
 koju ja imam prema tebi

1111
00:49:40,180 --> 00:49:41,000
 i ti prema meni

1112
00:49:41,000 --> 00:49:42,400
 to više govori

1113
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:44,040
 nego da te ozdravim

1114
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:45,680
 to je veći triumf ljubavi

1115
00:49:45,680 --> 00:49:48,540
 neće se sve vratit na staro

1116
00:49:48,540 --> 00:49:50,720
 sunce će ogranuti

1117
00:49:50,720 --> 00:49:53,540
 kada noć postane najdublja

1118
00:49:53,540 --> 00:49:57,240
 najdublja

1119
00:49:57,240 --> 00:49:57,860
 inače

1120
00:49:57,860 --> 00:49:59,100
 tik pred svitanje

1121
00:49:59,100 --> 00:50:00,040
 noć najdublja

1122
00:50:00,040 --> 00:50:02,080
 i najtamnija

1123
00:50:02,080 --> 00:50:04,460
 i sunce će ogranuti

1124
00:50:04,460 --> 00:50:07,420
 ali neće se stvari

1125
00:50:07,420 --> 00:50:08,940
 kako mi to mislimo

1126
00:50:08,940 --> 00:50:10,040
 odjednom nestati

1127
00:50:10,040 --> 00:50:11,840
 negdje ćemo šepati

1128
00:50:11,840 --> 00:50:12,980
 neki ćemo križ

1129
00:50:12,980 --> 00:50:14,740
 zagarliti u svom životu

1130
00:50:14,740 --> 00:50:16,400
 i kaže prorok Izaija

1131
00:50:16,400 --> 00:50:17,280
 i ti ćeš graditi

1132
00:50:17,280 --> 00:50:18,960
 na starim razvalinama

